$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
is_invited

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
is_invited -  This function allows you to check whether an invitation for a person is pending in a specific group.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int is_invited(string name,
object person)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the group
%^BOLD%^person%^RESET%^ - the person to be checked

.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if such an invitation exists, 0 if not

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/group_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function allows you to check whether an invitation for a
person is pending in a specific group.

.EP

